questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You need to have a hosting plan and a domain name, already purchased to get started. The content of your website is another thing that you may have at the time of purchasing the gig.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I don't have hosting account and domain yet?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It's not a problem. We can work on temporary domains which I always have and once you purchase your own we can shift the site there. THERE ARE NO EXTRA CHARGES FOR ALL OF THIS.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Have you worked with MLS / IDX integration?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yeah, I have worked with many MLS providers and IDX plugins. You have to contact me to see the samples.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I see the work you have done in the past?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I have multiple options in styling and designing the website and I can show you my past work in this niche as well. Contact me and see the great work I have done here for my clients.
